lso one of the best shows I’ve been to in a long time. This was my first time seeing Waterparks live, and the energy was insane from start to finish. \n\n\u003C/div>\n\n\u003Cdiv class=\"post-text\">\n\n## Show Details\n- **Artist:** Waterparks\n- **Tour:** The Prewler Tour UK/EU\n- **Venue:** La Machine du Moulin Rouge\n- **Location:** Paris, France\n- **Date:** 14 March 2026\n\n\u003C/div>\n\n---\n\n*For press passes or collabs: dilayduzler@gmail.com*","src/content/blog/waterparks-paris26.md","72e5ab30ee627328",{"html":48,"metadata":49},"\u003Ch2 id=\"gallery\">Gallery\u003C/h2>\n\u003Cdiv class=\"gallery-masonry\">\n  \u003Ca href=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-1.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-1.jpg\" alt=\"Waterparks live in Paris — photo 1\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-2.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-2.jpg\" alt=\"Waterparks live in Paris — photo 2\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-3.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-3.jpg\" alt=\"Waterparks live in Paris — photo 3\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-4.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-4.jpg\" alt=\"Waterparks live in Paris — photo 4\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-5.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-5.jpg\" alt=\"Waterparks live in Paris — photo 5\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  \u003C/a>\n  \u003Ca href=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-6.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    \u003Cimg src=\"/images/waterparks26/waterparks-6.jpg\" alt=\"Waterparks live in Paris — photo 6\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  \u003C/a>\